import React from 'react';
import Login from './Login';
import { AppRoute } from './AppRoute'
import StatiquePage from './StatiquePage';
import Clients from './Clients';
import ExplClient from './ExplClient';
import Demandes from './Demandes'
import ExplDemande from './ExplDemande'
import FeedBackClients from './FeedBackClients'
import ExplFeedBackClient from './ExplFeedBackClient'
import Services from './Services'
import AjoutService from './AjoutService'
import ModifService from './ModifService'
import ExplService from './ExplService'
import Travailleurs from './Travailleurs'
import ExplTravailleur from './ExplTravailleur'
import { Link, BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Switch, withRouter } from 'react-router-dom'

function App() {
  return (
    <Router>
      <Switch>
        <AppRoute path="/ExplFeedBackClient" component={ExplFeedBackClient} layout={StatiquePage} ></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/FeedBackClients" component={FeedBackClients} layout={StatiquePage} ></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/ExplTravailleur" component={ExplTravailleur} layout={StatiquePage} ></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/AjoutService" component={AjoutService} layout={StatiquePage} ></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/ModifService" component={ModifService} layout={StatiquePage} ></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/Travailleurs" component={Travailleurs} layout={StatiquePage} ></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/ExplService" component={ExplService} layout={StatiquePage} ></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/ExplDemande" component={ExplDemande} layout={StatiquePage} ></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/ExplClient" component={ExplClient} layout={StatiquePage} ></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/Demandes" component={Demandes} layout={StatiquePage} ></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/Services" component={Services} layout={StatiquePage} ></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/Clients" component={Clients} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <Route path="/" render={() => <Login />} />
      </Switch>
    </Router>
  );
}

export default App;
